Package: rseismTLS
Version: 1.0.0
Title: Induced Seismicity Traffic Light System
Description: Provides the tools to build a dynamic traffic light system (TLS) 
    to mitigate the risk of induced seismicity during underground stimulation 
    by fluid injection.
